<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Public Fruit Tree Map</title>
<style>
body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
text-align: center;
background:#f6f6f6;
}

h1{
margin-top:20px;
}

.map-container{
margin:auto;
width:90%;
